defs.docs: This crate provides a stable, safe and scoped threadpool.

defs.name: Pool
defs.docs:
A threadpool that acts as a handle to a number
 of threads spawned at construction.

defs.name: scoped

defs.name: Scope
defs.docs: Handle to the scope during which the threadpool is borrowed.
